feed.title: Wife of UPS pilot sues San Antonio company over fatal jet crash
feed.summary: The wife of a UPS pilot, Dana Justin Diamond, has filed a wrongful death lawsuit against ST Engineering San Antonio Aerospace, General Electric Co., and Boeing Co. following a fatal jet crash in Louisville, Kentucky.
